A 2017 brand relaunch included a new website that was first revealed for employees on Demo Kiosks set up at a Launch Party up in the San Francisco Skyline. After reviewing inital performance metrics and user experiences via HotJar Heat Maps and Google Analytics recorded sessions, revisions to the website were made to further define the success of maintaining user interest from  original content to related properties and the individuals that have contributed their points of view. Managed various HubSpot templates and sends for Internal and External communications 

* WordPress Theme Contributions 

* Single Property Pages Refinement

* Red Room Contributor Page

* The Red Room Video Player Up Next

* Contributor to Site Performance Audit/Analysis then directly translated into WordPress Theme Revisions  

* HubSpot Template Development / Content Management

